{"word":"G4845 - συμπληρόω - symplēróō - soom-play-ro'-o - Come","slug":"G4845","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμπληρόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>symplēróō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soom-play-ro'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Come"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BC;&#x03C0;&#x03BB;&#x03B7;&#x03C1;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - sumple&#x0304;roo&#x0304;</b> - <i>soom-play-ro'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G4137\">G4137</a>; to <i>implenish completely</i>, that is, (of space) to <i>swamp</i> (a boat), or (of time) to <i>accomplish</i> (passively be <i>complete</i>): - (fully) come, fill up."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1603\">G1603</a>, <a href=\"#/G1604\">G1604</a>, <a href=\"#/G378\">G378</a>, <a href=\"#/G4134\">G4134</a>, <a href=\"#/G4135\">G4135</a>, <a href=\"#/G4136\">G4136</a>, <a href=\"#/G4137\">G4137</a>, <a href=\"#/G4138\">G4138</a>, <a href=\"#/G466\">G466</a>"}]}